{"tid":428103,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日本新聞係咁報導場拳賽","createTime":"2017-10-07T20:09:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T00:55:49.000Z","uid":16724,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c9d2cbf16bec8227f3fec169198ac512efc45c2f","tid":428103,"uid":16724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T20:09:02.000Z","msg":"　世界ボクシング協会（WBA）スーパーフライ級元王者の河野公平（36）＝ワタナベ＝が7日、香港で世界ボクシング機構（WBO）同級2位で香港生まれのレックス・ツォーとの12回戦に臨み、相手が負傷して試合続行不能となり、7回途中までの判定で敗れた。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://headlines.yahoo.co.jp/hl?a=20171008-00000002-jij-spo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fheadlines.yahoo.co.jp%2Fhl%3Fa%3D20171008-00000002-jij-spo&d=Rn6nmUEmnPsVNQENRVnMODCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=ed37497f\" target=\"_blank\">https://headlines.yahoo.co.jp/hl?a=20171008-00000002-jij-spo</a><br />\n<br />\n純粹講返場比賽因為星如意外受傷唔可以繼續，最後判河野輸左。<br />\n<br />\n人地輸左果邊都冇出聲話場比賽唔公平，話星如贏得唔光彩，反而香港人就屌哂鬼，咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9693f87b87cab3da6be39f21c9b82bd0511dfc58","tid":428103,"uid":51932,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T00:09:47.000Z","msg":"新聞呀，會加其他感受評論落去嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7875a7359202990ee38bb6c4713c9547d240bf","tid":428103,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T00:13:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc126b3037e58d1a9145799425768e77aa9b2f4","tid":428103,"uid":45082,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T00:17:46.000Z","msg":"對個賽果公唔公平就無意見<br />\n但如果報導唔可以做到客觀同持平<br />\n咁不如唔好做新聞<br />\n你去post吓日本人嘅留言仲好<br />\n咁樣先反映到個實況"},{"pid":"573c97c19b740150a828e5c5d2899ed3e80ce01b","tid":428103,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T00:27:08.000Z","msg":"やっぱり中国圏とかになると、KOしないと、なかなか判定では勝てないなー<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6887c534eee7e679962ccdcba740155b8bcc45f0","tid":428103,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T00:34:17.000Z","msg":"唔知曹星如揀對手咪會中立去睇呢件事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d23c88dadadc8c105208658cc869c186b7a7db","tid":428103,"uid":66395,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T00:44:10.000Z","msg":"慘啦 柒到出日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b08bcfc37752ff891b6e1f1e2bdf4b09a46c4a","tid":428103,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T00:55:49.000Z","msg":"抵港狗去到日本俾日本人歧視<br />\n之前又空姐運黃金<br />\n呢單野又似十足支那狗咁<br />\n係支那運動員就撐左先<br />\n贏左就係到圍爐打飛機<br />\n輸左就好似上次李慧思果次咁<br />\n去人地荷蘭選手ig洗版<br />\n你地班港狗根本同支那狗一樣咁撚垃圾<br />\n抵你班港豬係日本機場俾人搜到仆街"}]}